            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="21076233">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/21076233/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p21076233-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 不可知論加上黑格兒經典辯論思維。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-09-13 19:02</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">3人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p21076233-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>不可知論加上黑格兒經典辯論思維。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

